de.patricklammers.vorlesungsplan.app.actionbar

Class SimpleMenuItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.patricklammers.vorlesungsplan.app.actionbar.SimpleMenuItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MenuItem

    public class SimpleMenuItem
extends Object
implements MenuItem
    A really dumb implementation of the MenuItem interface, that's only useful for our actionbar-compat purposes. See com.android.internal.view.menu.MenuItemImpl in AOSP for a more complete implementation.
